"sentence\": \"The friendship formed in the face of racism.\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 668, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Owens, a Black man, and Long, a white man from Germany, were fond of each other's victories regardless of criticism.\", \"from\": 669, \"to\": 785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 678, \"end\": 683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_people\", \"score\": 0.9933855464041628, \"rank\": 0.006656662494979937, \"text\": \"Black\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_people\"}, {\"begin\": 716, \"end\": 723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.9535412232980685, \"rank\": 0.0390228050208699, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of Owens' four gold medals at the Berlin Olympics came in the long jump, in which Long won silver,according to a report by ESPN.\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 914, \"end\": 918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"score\": 0.9999986621548796, \"rank\": 6.976510712832155e-07, \"text\": \"ESPN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When Jesse got the gold medal, my grandfather Luz went directly to him and embraced and congratulated him, because he thought it was an amazing ...\\\" said Long's granddaughter.\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 1097, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Hitler was at the stadium, and he did not like it, actually, so my grandfather got a call a few days afterwards never to embrace a negro again.\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1099, \"end\": 1105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adolf_Hitler\", \"score\": 0.9999999748304166, \"rank\": 2.5157084562485538e-08, \"text\": \"Hitler\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adolf_Hitler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adolf_Hitler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after the event, \\\"both really enjoyed it, had this medal celebration and went arm in arm through the stadium and were celebrating,\\\" Julia Long said.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1396, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch all the action from the Paris Olympic and Paralympic Games live on Peacock  Dortch told News4 that the moment in 1936 is relevant today.\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1428, \"end\": 1433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997928676053, \"rank\": 2.0713252273101537e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1471, \"end\": 1478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Love_Peacock\", \"score\": 0.5988268344613524, \"rank\": 0.6678250765070325, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Love_Peacock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Love_Peacock\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it proves that racism will not win,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1597, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Their story inspires people who may be bombarded with the fallacy of racial superiority,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1700, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I think my grandfather being there and winning four gold medals showed that Hitler was wrong.\\\"\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1800, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1782, \"end\": 1788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adolf_Hitler\", \"score\": 0.9999999748304166, \"rank\": 2.5157084562485538e-08, \"text\": \"Hitler\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adolf_Hitler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adolf_Hitler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both families have been watching the Olympics together and hope the friendship lasts through more generations.\", \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 1912, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The story never ends,\\\" Long said.\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1948, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The people really love the story, and it gives them hope and inspires them.\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 2025, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, it's wonderful to represent the Owens and Long family together.\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2072, \"end\": 2083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Long_family\", \"score\": 0.9999999375704667, \"rank\": 6.241876731911966e-08, \"text\": \"Long family\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Long_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Long_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it was very touching, very emotional.\\\"\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2135, \"entities\": []}]}"